headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Test Out New and Unreleased Cars on the Test Track
content: There’s nothing wrong with trying something on for size. You’d do it with a pair of pants at Binco, so why wouldn’t you do the same with a car? Stop by the Car Meet’s Test Track and rev the engine of the new Karin Sultan RS Classic, the upcoming Übermacht Cypher, and the Obey Tailgater S, at no cost to you – even if you scrape a little paint during a Time Trial or a Scramble.
